<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'Bahia: Culture & Depth' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- Journey Hero -->
  <section class="journey-hero section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="journey-hero-label">5-7 days</p>
      <h1>Bahia: Culture & Depth</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Salvador and beyond</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Opening -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <p class="journey-opening">Bahia is not one place.</p>
        <p>It's a region with different rhythms, from the intensity of Salvador to quieter coastal towns where time slows down.</p>
        <p>This journey is designed to move between these layers in a way that feels natural, not rushed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What This Is -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>What This Is</h2>
        <p>This is not just Salvador.</p>
        <p>It's an experience of Bahia that can include the city, but also extend beyond it, depending on how you want to travel.</p>
        <p>We shape the journey around a combination of:</p>
        <ul class="journey-list">
          <li>Salvador, for culture, history and energy</li>
          <li>Coastal areas for space, nature and slower pace</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Take Care Of / What You Experience -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-two-col">
        <div>
          <h2>What I Take Care Of</h2>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>Arrival into Salvador and local orientation</li>
            <li>Safe, well-positioned accommodation</li>
            <li>Movement between locations, carefully planned</li>
            <li>A structure that balances depth and ease</li>
            <li>Access to places and experiences that feel real</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>What You Experience</h2>
          <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-forest);">In Salvador</h4>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>The historic centre, with context</li>
            <li>Food rooted in Afro-Brazilian culture</li>
            <li>Music and rhythm as part of daily life</li>
          </ul>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-forest);">Beyond Salvador</h4>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>Quieter coastal towns</li>
            <li>Time near the sea, without the intensity of the city</li>
            <li>A slower pace that allows things to settle</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Difference -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>The Difference</h2>
        <p>Most people either stay only in Salvador or move through Bahia without structure.</p>
        <p>I create a flow between places, so the experience feels coherent.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who This Is For -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>Who This Is For</h2>
        <ul class="journey-list">
          <li>You want cultural depth</li>
          <li>You're open to moving between environments</li>
          <li>You don't want to manage logistics alone</li>
          <li>You want structure without rigidity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Changes -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>What Changes</h2>
        <p>You begin to understand Bahia as a whole.</p>
        <p>The contrasts make sense.<br>The experience connects.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="included-section">
        <div class="included-list">
          <h3>Your Investment Covers</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>5-7 nights of carefully selected accommodation</li>
            <li>Meals throughout your stay</li>
            <li>Internal transportation within Bahia</li>
            <li>All planned experiences and activities</li>
            <li>My guidance throughout the journey</li>
            <li>Local connections and introductions</li>
            <li>Translation and cultural navigation</li>
            <li>Pre-trip planning and customisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="included-list">
          <h3>Not Included</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>International flights to/from Brazil</li>
            <li>Travel insurance (required)</li>
            <li>Personal shopping and souvenirs</li>
            <li>Visa fees if applicable</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--color-warm-gray); font-size: 0.95rem;">I'm happy to advise on flight options and help with any logistics. Just ask.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>How We Begin</h2>
        <p>We start with a conversation. From there, I design the journey around you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Start the Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
